title: Week 4 Rankings 2022
description:
Field Yates, Stephania Bell and Daniel Dopp talk injuries, what level of panic you should have on some fantasy stars and who is going to have a breakout week. Plus, Liz Loza joins to give us some players who you need to be paying attention to this week.
